  "title": "Animated XP Bar",
  "description": "Makes the XP bar progress more satisfying to look at.",
  "body": "\n  <h3 style=\"line_height=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f515c01e2ca1b11b3a9eb5e1e74c0906173852d0_0.webp\" alt=\"\"></img>\n    &nbsp;Description&nbsp;\n    <br>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4b2e211dc4e3701c96ec4ec39975568ffe89c039.gif\" alt=\"\"></img>\n  </h3>\n\n  Adds an animation to the filled region of the XP bar, making it look more interesting and not just a flat PNG.\n  \n  <h3 style=\"line_height=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d365c94dde3f6a7d11d1a01b85419b24cfaffc7.png\" alt=\"\"></img>\n    &nbsp;Versions&nbsp;\n    <br>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4b2e211dc4e3701c96ec4ec39975568ffe89c039.gif\" alt=\"\"></img>\n  </h3>\n  \n  Currently supports Minecraft <strong>Java Edition 1.20.2 - 26.1</strong>.\n  \n  <h3 style=\"line_height=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cbf57578671ebac0913606bbb1059048846fb09d.png\" alt=\"\"></img> \n    &nbsp;Compatibility&nbsp;\n    <br> \n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4b2e211dc4e3701c96ec4ec39975568ffe89c039.gif\" alt=\"\"></img>\n  </h3>\n\n  Incompatible with any resource pack that modifies or animates the XP bar, such as rainbow XP bar packs.\n\n  <h3 style=\"line_height=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8acaa19ef612d00d44b369fd4feffedc08d90adb.png\" alt=\"\"></img>\n     &nbsp;Badges&nbsp; \n    <br> \n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4b2e211dc4e3701c96ec4ec39975568ffe89c039.gif\" alt=\"\"></img>\n  </h3>\n\n  <a href=\"https://patreon.com/Nerd_1023?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink\"><img alt=\"Support me on patreon\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/patreon-singular_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/m5AGYxRj3g\"><img alt=\"Join my discord\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\"></a>\n\n<br>\n\n## Want more XP Bar packs?\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/animated-xp-bar/\">\n\n![Animated XP Bar](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a086bb57eda1d0a5d98e5ac3d54249187aaf7d34.gif)\n\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/lava-xp\">\n\n![Lava XP Bar](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7274d284c329dbe9542f650566558a56273cb15f.gif)\n\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/stone-brick-xp-bar/\">\n\n  ![Stone Brick XP Bar](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1166a7d73761f469c0d532521679079c9343601f.png)\n  \n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/sculk-xp-bar/\">\n\n![Sculk XP Bar](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4bb4c39944af28ed79efa18881f60bcf3b9000f2.gif)\n\n</a>\n\n",
